id: "class:fighter#polearm_master"
name: "Polearm Master"
description: "The polearm master is schooled in the ancient wisdom that enemies are\
  \ best faced at the end of long striking pole, lashing like a serpent before clumsy\
  \ swords and axes can even be brought to bear."
